title: Warlock
description:
The earliest adventures of Adam Warlock, most recently seen in Guardians of the Galaxy.

This collection spans the '60s - '70s with help from shipjolly to fill in a key story; it was the Magus Saga which prompted me to track down all the pure digital files (not c2c scans) of Jim Starlin's messianic tale. The writing here would later shape his work on Dreadstar.

What issues I found will be complete storylines, but the collection isn't quite comprehensive. Missing are Fantastic Four 66 - 67 and Strange Tales 178 - 181 (the beginning of the Starlin run).

Thanks again to shipjolly for uploading Avengers Annual 07 for this; if any of you have the pure digital files that make this a complete collection, please remix and reup.
